"f96e8eef9b3391770980b142ee258dc269d278fb","tid":1480052,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba8913fe135984b8384e2e0689fb6cde2771c50","tid":1480052,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:57:03.000Z","msg":"LINDFOREIGNPRESSDOUWUITAIDOURSAITAU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"RSAITAU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"LUM JOR HO LOI RSAITAU HAI MUD SPRING <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a839ca095c4815c152b60212333249905dd5999","tid":1480052,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"NGOGINGYINTAIDUKMING"},{"pid":"7e9e06443a83a994c06e81e47089c0494a527834","tid":1480052,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de05f77ec189593f6311bcebefdaf7f43da9eeee","tid":1480052,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25cdae40b9d8bc6201e78666cffe76c8cfa9c94","tid":1480052,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1b57be5a489bc8ed134f0dbebb127d752ae638","tid":1480052,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"Wadiu, yung ho loi seen tai yuen<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>梁天琦封獄中信講過，政治就係要 <br />\n(1) 令支持嘅人繼續支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2) 拉返動搖嘅人過嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(3) 令唔支持我𡁻哋嘅人理解，繼而支持我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n贏係最緊要，民意係好重要嘅因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無可否認香港人係勇敢咗，但更多人仍然未有準備俾黑警追捕、食催淚彈、受傷、甚至被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要同政權講我哋唔割，我哋團結，發生咁多事依然團結一致反抗暴政，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就用最低門檻吸納最多人參加展示團結晒馬</strong></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁去維園坐、去集會就聚到最多人，老少咸宜<br />\n坐爆咗維園，就坐天后<br />\n坐爆咗天后，就坐銅鑼灣<br />\n如此類推，向西進發坐爆港島<br />\n好悶都唔走，互相幫助，傾計，坐到23:00<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要show團結，人數永遠都係政權最懼怕<br />\n目前關頭有人動搖，我哋要做最低門檻吸納最多人出席<br />\n怕俾人影大頭就戴黑超、戴帽、戴口罩，帶gear但唔主動上gear</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(商台有節目話811銅鑼灣有手足憶述有兩名身型極為高大健碩的黑衣人上前，命令他們前往尖沙咀，向他們喝斥：「你哋全副裝備唔係唔去尖沙咀呀嘛？」另一示威者指出，示威者只會商討行動，但不會命令，做法不尋常。阿欣表示，至晚上近10時，他們見現場已沒有太多示威者，於是換衫打算離開，並討論到哪裡吃晚飯，惟突然一群打扮與示威者相似但身型魁梧的黑衣人嘗試把他們制服，不足1分鐘即有速龍小隊現身配合。她稱被黑衣人以伸縮警棍攻擊，全身有7至8處棍傷。)詳細報導睇#4<br />\n<br />\n無可否認前排手足多次有勇有謀，行事理性。就算811手足冇行動諗住散，都會容易俾黑警target，或者被黑警慫恿去送頭。<del>加上全幪面/戴住gear做嘢係會大膽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n<br />\nQ: 你可能會話，依加普通集會已經唔安全，點都會行為藝術式着gear表態，唔着gear咪即係屈服？<br />\nA: 如果你認同818最緊要人多，人多先會離我哋目標近咗，咁懇請你做盡所有嘢令818多人，多宣傳，降低參與門檻<br />\n<br />\nQ: 你又可能會問，遊行係權利，佢剝奪/限制我哋就要順從，唔順從就俾黑警拘捕？咁樣同「鬧印度女仔做咩着得咁暴露出街，唔暴露就唔俾人強姦」blame the victim有咩分別？<br />\nA: 喺咁歪曲嘅社會堅持自己嘅權利真係好難。有少數女仔堅持着靚靚出街，但更多人真係明知咁樣強姦再blame the victim係唔啱，都寧願唔俾人強姦/姦殺而寧願着密實啲。同樣道理，大多數明知限制遊行係唔啱，但都怕受傷怕食彈怕被捕。如果你認同818呢一日要人多，人多先會離我哋目標近咗，咁懇請你做盡所有嘢令818多人，多宣傳，降低參與門檻。<br />\n<br />\nWill you give all you can give <br />\nSo that our banner may advance?<br />\n- 《Do you hear the people sing》<br />\n<br />\n建議文宣組多宣傳<span style=\"color: red;\">818可以點做，俾信心多啲人出嚟</span>：<br />\n- 齋坐齋企都可以塞爆港島<br />\n- 唔怕悶唔好走，一齊傾偈，坐到23:00<br />\n- 怕影大頭就cap+黑超+口罩<br />\n- 唔主動上gear (有tear gas先上)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">818係要show團結，冇得行就坐爆維園，唔夠坐就坐爆港島<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475691\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475691</a><br />\n-分享自LIHKG討論區<br />\n</span><br />\n歡迎討論，要屌求屌細力啲，一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"NGOJIGEIDOUHAI<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"BUDYUHELPTUIHAMYPOST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"Tuijor"},{"pid":"104c2f5da43681fac78dea2362d37a49ee086dcc","tid":1480052,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99e311ca211da4f15596236a1680b29d99d3800b","tid":1480052,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f96e8eef9b3391770980b142ee258dc269d278fb","tid":1480052,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba8913fe135984b8384e2e0689fb6cde2771c50","tid":1480052,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:57:03.000Z","msg":"LINDFOREIGNPRESSDOUWUITAIDOURSAITAU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"RSAITAU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"SORYEENOSPACEHOJENGAH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /